title: Thanh Hóa Stadium
text: The Thanh Hóa Stadium is a multi-use <a href="stadium">stadium</a> in <a href="Thanh%20H%C3%B3a">Thanh Hóa</a>, <a href="Vietnam">Vietnam</a>. It is currently used mostly for <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> matches and is the home stadium of <a href="%C4%90%C3%B4ng%20%C3%81%20Thanh%20H%C3%B3a%20F.C.">Thanh Hóa F.C.</a> of the <a href="V.League%201">V.League 1</a>. The stadium holds 14,000 spectators.
